positions.description: Shift Supervisor, training, maintain overall security of distribution and corporate campus, ensured the C-TPAT (Customs-Trade Partnership Against Terrorism guidelines for security were met and upheld, security patrol by foot, security patrol by vehicle, provided expertise and knowledge in updating policies and procedures.
positions.title: Security Officer/Team Leader/Shift Supervisor

positions.description:
Supervise and control inmate behavior, exercise appropriate judgment in handling of special needs situations or inmates; provide 
assistance in classification of inmates, communicate effectively and coherently with other staff or inmates, demonstrate effective communicative skills with inmates, public and staff, perform searches of people, cells, objects capable of concealing contraband, and indoor and outdoor areas, administer basic emergency first aid, transport or escort inmates (hostile, aggressive, passive, etc.) using handcuffs and other approved restraints in accordance to policy and procedure, read and comprehend legal and non-legal documents, maintain weapons, equipment and uniforms in functional condition as prescribed for by 
departmental policy, maintain inmate property and storage, collect, resolve and/or direct to appropriate individual or division, inmate complaints, grievances or requests, prepare investigative and other reports or documentation, using appropriate grammar, endure verbal and mental abuse when confronted with hostile views or opinions of inmates and other persons in an antagonistic environment, process and release inmates including taking photographs and legible sets of inked fingerprints, and/or palm prints.
positions.title: Detention Officer

positions.description: Certified Boarding Officer (Federal Law Enforcement Officer), Command representative (in their absence), Duty section leader, tactical boat coxswain, boat coxswain, boat crewman, maintain, carried and usage of M-9 Beretta, P229 DAK Sig 40 cal., M-16A2 rifle, M-14T rifle, M-240 automatic machine gun, 12 gauge modified police riot shotgun, maintenance and beautification of Coast Guard boats
positions.title: Boatswain's Mate
